{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1191112, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 235072, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得乘客的做法确实是符合规则的，但是司机态度差也完全能理解，就好像我点了一盘菜付了钱当着厨师的面倒掉也不违反任何规则，但是也非常值得厨师把我骂一顿了", "timestamp": 1614854396, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1191123, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 235072, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "自私的人自有自私的人为了自己的自私而替她辩护", "timestamp": 1614854451, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1191146, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 235072, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 以及他", "timestamp": 1614854635, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1191183, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 235072, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在dz看来什么规定40min超时罚款而36min不到40min所以司机没理由生气，就跟在一个实际问题上讨论“真空中的球形鸡”如何如何一样离谱。", "timestamp": 1614854875, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1191186, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 235072, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以为什么没人冲货拉拉啊？", "timestamp": 1614854893, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1191196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 235072, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 货拉拉最该冲，实际上有载客的职能，就该做出载客相应的安全防护措施。", "timestamp": 1614854971, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1191348, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 235072, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有理由生气，但是不能转嫁到消费者身上。", "timestamp": 1614856159, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1191360, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 235072, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 打车让司机等5分钟那种，很多司机不耐烦就取消订单了。", "timestamp": 1614856252, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1191402, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 235072, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 同意Eve", "timestamp": 1614856570, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 235072, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "货拉拉的事情，觉得责怪司机态度有问题的人蛮离谱的，不知道是没有打过车么。别说等36min了，就是让司机等个5分钟，能有几个司机给好脸色（当然，出租车周转快很短时间就是一单，虽然货拉拉周转没那么快，但36min加上下车可能浪费的时间，确实非常影响司机赚钱）。", "timestamp": 1614854217, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1614856572, "url": "", "vote": {}}}